            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Un programa como ese utiliza el operador <code>==</code> para verificar si la <code>answer</code> de un concursante a un cuestionario de trivia es correcta.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" answer = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Picasso&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" answer == \" /><text value=\"&quot;Picasso&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;\\(answer) is correct!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"33\" endIndex=\"35\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Picasso is correct!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>==</code>.</p></body></html>"
