            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>¿Qué pasa si la respuesta del cuestionario de trivia no es correcta? Podemos usar <code>!=</code> para verificar si <code>answer</code> no es igual a <code>\"Picasso\"</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" answer = \" /><text value=\"&quot;Matisse&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" answer != \" /><text value=\"&quot;Picasso&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(answer + \" /><text value=\"&quot; is wrong!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"26\" endIndex=\"45\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"answer == &quot;Picasso&quot;\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Matisse is wrong!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>answer != \"Picasso\"</code>.</p></body></html>"
