          {
            "title": "Different comparisons",
            "id": 126743,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>  Las declaraciones <code>if</code> funcionan con todos los operadores de comparación que hemos explorado hasta ahora. Como verificar si <code>age</code> es mayor o igual a <code>55</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" age = \" /><text value=\"75\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" age &gt;= \" /><text value=\"55\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\" {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Discount applied&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"16\" endIndex=\"19\" /><option startIndex=\"20\" endIndex=\"22\" /><option startIndex=\"23\" endIndex=\"25\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"&lt;=\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Discount applied\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>age</code> seguido de <code>&gt;=</code> y finalmente <code>55</code>.</p></body></html>"
          },
          {
            "title": "Condition",
            "id": 126744,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>  Las sentencias <code>if</code> no tienen que usar un operador especial para comparar variables como <code>isDay</code> con valores booleanos.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" isDay = \" /><text value=\"true\" class=\"literal\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" isDay {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(\" /><text value=\"&quot;Lights off!&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"20\" endIndex=\"25\" /><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"true\" /></content></option><option correct=\"false\"><content><text value=\"==\" /></content></option></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"Lights off!\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>isDay</code>.</p></body></html>"
