            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Para usar el resultado de una comparación varias veces, podemos almacenarlo en una variable como <code>pass</code>.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"swift\" name=\"main.swift\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" score = \" /><text value=\"51\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"let\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" pass = score &gt; \" /><text value=\"50\" class=\"number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"if\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" pass {\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"print\" class=\"built_in\" /><text value=\"(pass)\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"}\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"validatedInput\" isDefault=\"true\" startIndex=\"40\" endIndex=\"44\" /></interactions><output><content><text value=\"true\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Asegúrese de elegir <code>pass</code>.</p></body></html>"
